{
    "name": "Influencer",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Influencers build their reputations as subject matter and lifestyle experts. They inspire their followers to mirror the example they set, whether that means cooking the same recipes, adopting the same magical shortcuts, or assuming the same political stance. They act as advocates, reviewers, and brand ambassadors. However, they must sustain viewership and their reputations, and any threat to either of these can transform the influencer into an implacable foe. An accomplished influencer wields fearsome power, potentially generating or crushing demand for a new product."
        },
        {
            "name": "Celebrities",
            "type": "section",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Interstellar Species",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Interstellar Species pg. 156",
                        "alt": "Interstellar Species pg. 156",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq02d4w?Starfinder-Interstellar-Species"
                    },
                    "page": 156
                }
            ],
            "html": "Celebrities shine in ways that often draw admiration, adoration, or amusement from fans across their home worlds and beyond. They regularly engage with fans through interviews, social media, and special appearances, boosting their sway in the court of public opinion. Some celebrities use their massive platforms to influence policy and elections, and it\u2019s not uncommon for groups with specific political or corporate interests to secretly plant or sponsor celebrities to advance particular agendas."
        }
    ],
